{"tid":2408070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[以事論事] 班成日屌人恐懼撚/防疫撚既無懼撚真係好撚煩","createTime":"2021-02-14T14:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T16:31:38.000Z","uid":30274,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e65de0a469b3047720977c562c597ce5c5a4ad0","tid":2408070,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"以事論事<br />\n隻毒咁勁咁得人驚<br />\n大家點解唔好好抗疫，點解唔聽話留喺屋企唔禁足?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出街食飯，去商場迫，入長洲西貢，有冇紀錄自己行蹤? 萬一爆發，點搵大家出黎集中送去隔離營?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然至今10,780確診，10,185出院，比率係94.5%，但即係仲有5.5%出唔到院，有成193人死，又雖然死既絕大部份唔係老人家就長期病患，其他人染到最多都係發燒咳兩聲或完全冇徵狀，但始終即係有人死，仲可以話唔驚? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時醫院病房爆滿，醫療體系崩潰，對唔對得住醫護，對唔對得住手足?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察去哂邊? 呢啲人好自私，肆意播毒，擺明違反限聚令，快啲拉哂佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇戴好口罩，拉! 入店舖唔自動嘟體溫錶，拉! 超過上限群聚人數，拉!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻毒好勁好得人驚，大家一定要齊心抗疫!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢啲唔係話支持政府，係客觀以事論事，對事不對人，是其是，非其非，港共啲監控措施，限制人身自由政策，但真係對抗疫有用，手足大家幫幫手ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班友，一係就屌人口罩法西斯，一係就自己唔戴好口罩，一定係熱狗，只要係熱狗，就一定講乜做乜都係錯，大家一齊落力啲屌鳩佢地，恥笑佢地!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地雖然唔單止自己戴好，仲會屌鳩人唔戴好，不過我地唔係口罩法西斯! 我地冇配合政府抗疫! 只不過好撚驚感染，隻毒真係好得人驚, 唔係講笑!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無懼撚唔驚咪唔好戴，不過我會屌鳩你唔戴，然後比狗拉比政府告，罰錢坐監，我會笑鳩柒你政府警察好波! 捉鳩哂呢啲人!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再講一次我唔係支持政府，疫情好嚴峻，只係防疫為健康，完全係兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8dd8506845a89753cb04adb0b198dccc0f57f4","tid":2408070,"uid":30274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b696ad2a3a2672f7fb89904b9700d5ecec9ca2","tid":2408070,"uid":30274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba913358aa0a49a089fbe469b63d8b2a8fe12a0b","tid":2408070,"uid":30274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9851bb7ec285106ccf0903005df5d7b0d735055","tid":2408070,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌鳩你地"},{"pid":"b9323ce647f038c9d0dd7cf2a865b18540bba224","tid":2408070,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a720031017c7dced450a6